    "content": "[Intro]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--5p4------------------------|\r\nD|--------5p3------------------|\r\nA|--------------5p4------------|\r\nE|-----------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-5----5--4-------3-------3--2----------5----5--4-------3-------3--2--3----4-|\r\nE|------------5-------5------------3----------------5-------5-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verses & Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|5---5-----------------------3----5-----5-------------------------3------5--|\r\nE|------5-----5--3-----3--5-----------------5------5--3------3--5------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Pre-Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------5-------------------7------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------5-----5-------------7-----7-----5------5--4----4--3----3--2-------|\r\nE|--3---------------3----5--------------5-------------------------------0--1-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------------7----|\r\nD|------------5-------------------7------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------5-----5-------------7-----7-----5------5--5----5--5----5--5-------|\r\nE|--3---------------3----5--------------5----------------------------------0-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------5--------------------7------------------------------|\r\nA|---------5-----5--------------7-----7--------5---------3--5-----|\r\nE|--3---------------3----5---------------5------------5-----------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Solo]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------12--14h15--14--------12--------------12------------|\r\nD|--12--12--14--15---------------------------15--14--15------12--------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|---------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---14/15--14--12--14--15h14--12--14/19v---17p15--17--15--17/19--19v--|\r\nD|12-------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|---------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--17p15--17--15--14--15--14--15--17--15--14--12---------------14\\----|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------15--14--15---------|\r\nA|------------------------------------------------------------------5--|\r\nE|---------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n*************************\r\n\r\np = pull off\r\n/ = slide up\r\nh = hammer on\r\nv = vibrato\r\n\\ = slide down\r\n\r\n*************************\r\n\r\n\r\nThe VERSE/CHORUS section is just the basic idea to start with.\r\nListen to the tune and you will easily find the little fills Paul uses to\r\nfunk it up. Doesn't have to be identical to sound really good.\r\nJust stick to the melody and remember the song is in Dm. This is my\r\nfirst tab ever, so please rate and comment/correct it!\r\nOne of my favorite songs and artists, so it was worth pouring over to\r\ntry to give the most helpful & accurate tab.",
